# A009-11 (audit #8): pin text files to LF in the working tree so agent edits and baseline
# restores never pick up CRLF under core.autocrlf=true. The study's baseline gate hashes
# prompts/system_prompt.md as raw LF bytes; without this, `git checkout` smudged it to CRLF
# and broke the locked-hash check. Combined with edit_applier writing newline="".
*.py   text eol=lf
*.md   text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.jsonl text eol=lf
*.txt  text eol=lf
